parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front differential can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations, especially when driving at high speeds. This can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding or whining noise from the front of the vehicle
sudden loss of power
wheels locking up
vehicle veering or skidding
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-miss situations, especially when driving at high speeds. This can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding or whining noise from the rear of the vehicle
sudden loss of power
wheels locking up
vehicle veering or skidding
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and engine components can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to accidents or near-miss situations, especially when driving at high speeds. This can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle rolling forward while the brake pedal is engaged
sudden loss of power
difficulty shifting gears
and unusual noises from the engine or transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column lock can cause the steering wheel to lock, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks
the key will not turn in the ignition
the steering wheel is stuck in an upward position
the vehicle will not start
the steering wheel shakes uncontrollably during high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the air suspension system can cause the vehicle to bounce erratically, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle bounces erratically at all road surfaces
the front end of the vehicle collapses while parked
excessive strain on ball joints and front control arms.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the differential can cause loud humming sounds, which can be a precursor to more serious problems.
symptoms: Loud humming sounds from the differential.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the steering wheel to shake uncontrollably, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel shakes uncontrollably during high speeds
a loud "knocking" sound is heard during low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag light is on
airbag does not deploy in a crash
cracking or fracture of the dashboard around the airbag system
passenger occupancy sensor failure
seatbelt warning light does not illuminate
intermittent airbag warning light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard around the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy prematurely or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Cracking or fracture of the dashboard around the airbag system
airbag light is on
airbag does not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag light is on
passenger occupancy sensor failure
intermittent airbag warning light.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Loss of Power and Engine Stalling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power and engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle cuts off while driving
the vehicle stalls
the vehicle loses power
the parking brake warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power and mobility, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle goes into limp mode
the transmission fails
the vehicle loses power
the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear differential failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: A loud abnormal noise is heard from the rear of the vehicle
the rear differential fails
the vehicle vibrates or shakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Suspension failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's suspension drops or collapses
the vehicle's suspension fails
the vehicle's air shocks malfunction
the vehicle's suspension sensor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including warning indicators illuminating on the instrument panel, loss of power, and electrical damage to wiring, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: All warning indicators illuminate on the instrument panel
vehicle will not continuously run
battery drains every night and every time the vehicle is parked
random tire pressure system failure codes
loss of power associated with the ignition switch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the fuel pump to fail, leading to engine stalling, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Fuel pump failure
overheating and melting of the plastic surrounding the copper feedthru pins connecting the fuel pump to the fuel pump relay
undersized pins and sockets in the fuel pump power and fuel level sensor electrical connector.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sunroof drain tube can cause water to accumulate and damage electrical components, leading to electrical failures and potential accidents.
symptoms: Sunroof drain tube becomes dry and rough over time
causing the elbow attached to the side fender to break off
water accumulates in the passenger side floor
electrical damage to wiring that controls windows
chairs
and sunroof.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the keyless entry system can cause the doors to lock and prevent exit, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Doors will not unlock manually
only unlock using the keyless entry remote
security feature on the keyless entry prevents manual unlocking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heated windshield can cause smoke to come from the passenger side door and failure of side mirrors, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Smoke comes from the passenger side door
side mirrors fail to move
internal failure of the electric heated windshield.
